org.jconfigurations.converters.ConfigurationConverter

  • Packages that use ConfigurationConverter 
    Package Description
    org.jconfigurations.configurators
    Contains the Configurator interface and all its implementations.
    org.jconfigurations.converters
    Contains the ConfigurationConverter interface and its implementations.
    org.jconfigurations.functions
    Contains functions used by the framework, most of which implement the custom ErrorFunction.

      Subinterfaces of ConfigurationConverter in org.jconfigurations.converters 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  CollectionConfigurationConverter<T>
      CollectionConfigurationConverters are used by configurators to convert a configuration value into an instance of a Collection of type T.
      interface  MapConfigurationConverter<K,V>
      MapConfigurationConverters are used by configurators to convert a configuration value into an instance of a Map of types K and V.
